Phoenix sees that she's hurt him, but isn't sure what to do.  "I'm 
sorry," she says.  "It really bothers me, knowing that I care about 
you but not why.  The Rogues did this," she indicates her altered 
state, with the weapons and the new beast form, "to me.  I think they 
deleted my memories, too."  A tear rolls down her cheek.
